Task 2: File and Directory Operations
Subtask 2.1: List Files and Directories with Get-ChildItem
Basic Directory Listing
List contents of the current directory:
Get-ChildItem
Use the alias for shorter commands:
ls
List contents with detailed information:
Get-ChildItem -Force
Advanced Listing Options
List only directories:
Get-ChildItem -Directory
List only files:
Get-ChildItem -File
List contents recursively (including subdirectories):
Get-ChildItem -Recurse
Filter files by extension:
Get-ChildItem *.txt
List hidden files and directories:
Get-ChildItem -Hidden
Subtask 2.2: Create Files and Directories with New-Item
Creating Directories
Create a new directory for lab exercises:
