PowerShell Syntax Rules
Cmdlet Structure: Verb-Noun format (Get-ChildItem, New-Item)
Parameters: Use -ParameterName Value format
Variables: Start with $ symbol
Comments: Use # for single-line comments
String Interpolation: Use "$variable" for variable expansion
